interpretation: The goblin emoji represents mischief and trickery. It warns of deceitful behavior and urges you to be cautious of those who may be trying to deceive you. This card also signifies the need to be aware of your own actions and intentions, as they may have unintended consequences. The goblin can represent a mischievous or playful spirit, but it can also signify darker energies and malevolent intentions. In a reading, this card may suggest that you need to confront your fears or confront someone who is causing you harm. It can also indicate a need for you to be more assertive in protecting your own interests. Overall, the goblin emoji reminds us to be wary of those who may be trying to deceive us and to stay vigilant in protecting ourselves from harm.
